reviewText: I had been looking for this music for several years. The tape was in mint condition and the shipment was fast. This is a collector's item so I should have contacted Amazon first! Amazon and your suppliers, you have made a believer out of me.

This video is wonderfully done.  The songs done on this video have a wonderful mix of harmony and blend.  I really enjoyed this video and wish that others will review it.  It really blessed me and I know it will bless  you, too.
